ZH: 我喜欢在沙滩上晒太阳。
EN: I like to sunbathe on the beach.

ZH: 每天晒太阳可以帮助身体吸收足够的维生素D。
EN: Sunbathing every day can help your body absorb enough vitamin D.

ZH: 她在花园里晒太阳，感觉很舒服。
EN: She is sunbathing in the garden and feels very comfortable.

ZH: 他喜欢在草地上躺着晒太阳。
EN: He likes to lie on the grass and sunbathe.

ZH: 孩子们经常在游泳池边晒太阳。
EN: The children often sunbathe by the pool.

ZH: 她脸上晒得有点红。
EN: She got a bit sunburnt on her face.

ZH: 晒太阳对皮肤有益处，但记得涂防晒霜。
EN: Sunbathing is good for the skin, but remember to apply sunscreen.

ZH: 我很长时间没有晒太阳了，感觉皮肤很苍白。
EN: I haven't sunbathed for a long time and my skin feels pale.

ZH: 家里的阳台是我最喜欢的晒太阳的地方。
EN: The balcony at home is my favorite place to sunbathe.

ZH: 在海边散步、晒太阳真是一种享受。
EN: Walking by the sea and sunbathing is really enjoyable.

ZH: 晒太阳会增加人体内的维生素D含量。
EN: Sunbathing can increase the levels of vitamin D in the body.

ZH: 在户外运动之后，晒太阳可以帮助恢复体力。
EN: Sunbathing can help to recover energy after outdoor activities.

ZH: 我看到周围人都在公园里晒太阳，也想去。
EN: I see everyone around me sunbathing in the park and I also want to go.

ZH: 晒太阳的最佳时间是上午十点至下午四点。
EN: The best time to sunbathe is between 10 AM and 4 PM.

ZH: 我希望能找到一个安静的地方在那里晒太阳。
EN: I hope to find a quiet place where I can sunbathe.

ZH: 晒太阳可以改善心情，让人感到放松。
EN: Sunbathing can improve mood and make people feel relaxed.

ZH: 在阳光下晒太阳是一种享受自然的方式。
EN: Sunbathing in the sunlight is a natural way to enjoy.

ZH: 晒太阳时，要注意补充水分，避免中暑。
EN: When sunbathing, remember to drink plenty of fluids to avoid heatstroke.

